Revision history for Perl extension Attribute-TieClasses

1.100710  2010-03-12 16:07:34 Europe/Vienna
    - converted the distribution to Dist::Zilla-style
    - requires perl 5.8
    - Used clearer names for subroutines, also to keep pod-spell happy.

0.05  Thu Jul 25 15:27:43 CEST 2008 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - Changed dist style and Changes back to standard. People didn't like it -
       the nail that sticks out gets hammered down.
     - Added standard test files; this will also help with CPANTS.

